{"documentCount":11,"nextId":11,"documentIds":{"0":"about/","1":"genres/blues/","2":"genres/classical/","3":"genres/electronic/","4":"genres/folk/","5":"genres/hip-hop/","6":"genres/jazz/","7":"genres/pop/","8":"genres/rap/","9":"genres/rock/","10":"index.html"},"fieldIds":{"title":0,"headings":1,"text":2},"fieldLength":{"0":[1,12,83],"1":[2,3,33],"2":[2,3,35],"3":[2,3,33],"4":[2,3,37],"5":[3,4,36],"6":[2,3,33],"7":[2,3,33],"8":[2,3,31],"9":[2,3,35],"10":[1,15,93]},"averageFieldLength":[1.9090909090909092,5,43.81818181818182],"storedFields":{"0":{"title":"About","id":"about/","text":"About All-things-Music\nWhat is All-things-Music?\nAll-things-Music is a community-driven website that documents a wide variety of songs across many different genres. It provides a friendly experience that allows users to easily explore and discover a diverse range of music.\nOur Goal\nHere at All-things-Music, our goals are to:\nCreate a welcoming collaborative environment\nDocument our community’s favourite songs\nShare favourites within the the community\nIntroduce a more diverse musical experience to our users\n\nWhy we Do What we Do\nWe believe that by recording favourite songs within our community, our users will discover a far wider variety of music than they otherwise would.\nContributing\nIf you would like to add to All-things-Music’s collection of songs, visit our GitHub repository and follow the listed contribution guidelines.\n"},"1":{"title":"Blues Music","id":"genres/blues/","text":"Blues\nThe home base for all things blues music\nThis page records all kinds of blues songs expressing struggle and triumph from all around the world.\nSong Name\nLittle Red Rooster by Howlin’ Wolf (1961).\n\nSong Name\n…\n"},"2":{"title":"Classical Music","id":"genres/classical/","text":"Classical\nThe home base for all things classical music\nThis page records all kinds of classical songs celebrating different cultures from all around the world.\nSong Name\nCello Suite No. 1 by Johann Sebastian Bach (1717-1723).\nSong Name\n…\n"},"3":{"title":"Electronic Music","id":"genres/electronic/","text":"Electronic\nThe home base for all things electronic music\nThis page records all kinds of electronic songs, from house to hardcore, techno to trance, and many more.\nSong Name\nClarity by Zedd Feat. Foxes (2012).\nSong Name\n…\n"},"4":{"title":"Folk Music","id":"genres/folk/","text":"Folk\nThe home base for all things folk music\nThis page records all kinds of folk songs telling the stories and experiences of a people or culture from all around the world.\nSong Name\nBlowin’ in the Wind by Bob Dylan (1962).\nSong Name\n…\n"},"5":{"title":"Hip-Hop Music","id":"genres/hip-hop/","text":"Hip-Hop\nThe home base for all things hip-hop music\nThis page docuements all kinds of hip-hop songs, including rap, trap, and many more genres.\nSong Name\nParents Just Don’t Understand by Will Smith (1988).\nSong Name\n…\n"},"6":{"title":"Jazz Music","id":"genres/jazz/","text":"Jazz\nThe home base for all things jazz music\nThis page holds all kinds of jazz songs, such as bebop, electro-swing, and many more genres.\nSong Name\nRound Midnight by Thelonious Monk (1944).\nSong Name\n…\n"},"7":{"title":"Pop Music","id":"genres/pop/","text":"Pop\nThe home base for all things pop music\nThis page holds all kinds of pop songs, with genres such as dance, rock and roll, and many more.\nSong Name\nBlinding Lights by The Weeknd (2020).\nSong Name\n…\n"},"8":{"title":"Rap Music","id":"genres/rap/","text":"Rap\nThe home base for all things rap music\nThis page records all kinds of rap songs centered around rhythm and rhymes from all around the world.\nSong Name\nMiami by Will Smith (1998).\nSong Name\n…\n"},"9":{"title":"Rock Music","id":"genres/rock/","text":"Rock\nThe home base for all things rock music\nThis page holds all kinds of rock songs, including genres such as alternative, math rock, metal, and many more.\nSong Name\nSweet Home Alabama by Lynyrd Skynyrd (1974).\nSong Name\n…\n"},"10"